    <h1 class="mb-4">Data Types Information</h1>
    <p><strong>age:</strong> Represents an integer value between 18 and 99 (inclusive).</p>
    <p><strong>name:</strong> Represents a random name string.</p>
    <p><strong>email:</strong> Represents a random email address.</p>
    <p><strong>password:</strong> Represents a random password.</p>
    <p><strong>phone:</strong> Represents a random phone number.</p>
    <p><strong>birthday:</strong> Represents a random past date as a birthday.</p>
    <p><strong>address:</strong> Represents a random street address.</p>
    <p><strong>country:</strong> Represents a random country name.</p>
    <p><strong>street:</strong> Represents a random street name.</p>
    <p><strong>zipcode:</strong> Represents a random ZIP code.</p>
    <p><strong>gender:</strong> Represents a random gender ('Male' or 'Female').</p>
    <p><strong>generic:</strong> Represents a generic faker data type based on the specified field.</p>
